						<p>Same wall.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">No king: Dundhubhi, Āvaṇi.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription records a gift of 10 <hi rend="italic">paṇam</hi> by a certain Padari of the <hi rend="italic">Veḷḷāḻa</hi> community, named Nalliśaiyāḷaṉ Parākkiramaṉ of Pālatoḻuvu in Kuṟuppu-nāḍu for a <hi rend="italic">sandhyā</hi> lamp given by the donor to the god Aviṉāśiyāḷuḍaiya-nāyaṉār.</p>						

